long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Wikistar - Star Wikipedia Pages - github style star buttons for wikipedia pages for you stargazer homies out there.

Save and star your favorite Wikipedia pages. Basically bookmark and organize the articles you find most interesting or useful for future reference.
